m><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"32b4d298892248ad52bac9f4cb36632c83917d3c","tid":1667182,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8158f8284f3771aedcbae3a61bcb1f0f7614a8fb","tid":1667182,"uid":283507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T10:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6NLCDOp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6NLCDOp.jpg&h=012859c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GSxsGK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GSxsGK.jpg&h=03861696&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T13:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1124b9475ade1cd2a5bd027f60063478c232ad6","tid":1667182,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8158f8284f3771aedcbae3a61bcb1f0f7614a8fb","tid":1667182,"uid":283507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"201